    <item>
      <title>多诺霍称特朗普新总统任期对欧洲来说是“严重问题”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/new-trump-presidency-is-serious-issue-for-europe-donohoe-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元集团主席帕斯查尔·多诺霍表示，唐纳德·特朗普可能再次出任总统，这将促使欧盟做好准备，减少经济对美国的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/new-trump-presidency-is-serious-issue-for-europe-donohoe-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求企业审查债券基金期限以控制风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-tells-firms-to-screen-bond-fund-duration-to-curb-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国监管机构已要求一些基金管理公司报告新债券基金产品的期限，这是抑制市场风险的最新举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-tells-firms-to-screen-bond-fund-duration-to-curb-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚利用国家资金在国内投资 270 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/malaysia-taps-state-funds-to-invest-27-billion-domestically</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚财政部周四表示，马来西亚正在制定一项计划，利用国家相关基金在未来五年内向当地进行 1200 亿林吉特（270 亿美元）的直接投资，以“促进关键经济领域的增长”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/malaysia-taps-state-funds-to-invest-27-billion-domestically</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国有银行在牛市中加大债券销售力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-seven-year-yield-rises-most-since-april-amid-pushback-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员表示，中国大型国有银行周四上午大规模出售七年期国债，这一迹象表明当局抑制创纪录债务上涨的举措正在升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-seven-year-yield-rises-most-since-april-amid-pushback-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:30:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼盾兑美元汇率自 5 月以来首次突破 16,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rupiah-rises-past-16-000-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走弱，且印尼官员早前采取措施平息投资者对新政府财政政策的担忧，印尼盾兑美元汇率突破了 16,000 的关键关口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rupiah-rises-past-16-000-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:22:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
